Name: Andersen Vs Stability AI
Court: Northern District Of California
Year: 2023
Isssues: class action over training models on copyrighted works, copyright over including the work in a training set, claims the models contain copies of the work in order to reproduce.
Results: Many claims but not all dismissed. On-going, Discovery starts September 8th 2026.
Source: https://www.courtlistener.com/docket/66732129/andersen-v-stability-ai-ltd/

Name: Doe (1-5) Vs Github
Court: Northern District Of California
Year: 2022
Issues: Code scraping and reproduction without attribution is a copyright violation
Results: Some claims dismissed but not all. On-going, before appeals court.
Source: https://www.courtlistener.com/docket/69495342/doe-et-al-v-github-inc-et-al/

Name: Getty Images Vs Stability AI
Court: Northern District Of California
Year: 2025
Issues: Claims Model Copied copyrighted works for training, outputted works to compete with original works.
Results: On-going, no major decisions.
Source: https://www.courtlistener.com/docket/71112094/getty-images-us-inc-v-stability-ai-ltd/
Note: The 2023 case in the District Of Delaware is related as is a near identical claim in 2023 in the UK.

